<hw>Ice"quake`</hw> <pr>(⟦imac⟧s"kw⟦amac⟧k`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>The crash or concussion attending the breaking up of masses of ice,
-- often due to contraction from extreme cold.</def>⟦br⟧
